He faces a crimen injuria charge for his racist rant while on holiday in Greece last year. #Dstv403 JOHANNESBURG - Adam Catzavelos' legal team says he is also facing prosecution in Greece. He has been served with papers in that country which need to be translated to English. Catzavelos faces a crimen injuria charge in South Africa for his racist rant while on holiday in Greece last year. READ: The sad truth about the Catzavelos video The businessman made a video, which went viral, where he used the K-word repeatedly. He made a brief appearance at the Randburg Magistrates Court on Thursday where the matter was postponed to 10 July.